dct_description_sm: Compass rose, figurative illustration, coats of arms.
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Upper right corner: compass rose indicating the position of Malta with reference to Italy and Sicily.
Upper left corner: a 41-point key to the city including important sites.
Lower right corner: decorative cartouche containing the islands of Malta and Gozo.
